      "text": "",
      "subsections": {
        "Vitamin_Prophylaxis_for_Chronic_alcoholics": {
          "text": "At risk for\nthiamine deficiency\n, but no symptoms:\nthiamine\n100mg PO q day\nGive multivitamin PO; patient at risk for other vitamin deficiencies",
          "tables": []
        },
        "Banana_bag": {
          "text": "The majority of chronic\nalcoholics\ndo\nNOT\nrequire a\nbanana bag\n[3]\n[4]\nThiamine\n100mg IV\nFolate\n1mg IV (cheaper PO)\nMultivitamin 1 tab IV (cheaper PO)\nMagnesium sulfate\n2mg IV\nNormal saline\nas needed for hydration",
          "tables": []
        }
